# Digital App Game Marketplace

## Student Information
- Faculty Number: 2401321033
- Name: Eren Yashar

## Project Description
This is a full-stack digital game marketplace system.

It consists of:
- ASP.NET Core Web API (Backend)
- ASP.NET MVC (Frontend)
- JWT Authentication
- CRUD operations for Products, Users, Purchases

## Features
- User registration and login (JWT)
- Product management (CRUD)
- Purchase system
- Pagination and sorting
- Secure API endpoints

## Technologies Used
- ASP.NET Core Web API
- ASP.NET MVC
- Entity Framework Core
- SQLite
- JWT Authentication

## How to Run

### Backend (API)
1. Open API project
2. Run: dotnet run
3. Swagger: https://localhost:7056/swagger
---

### Frontend (MVC)
1. Open Web project
2. Run: dotnet run
3. Open: https://localhost:7179/Products
